  <brief_title>Non Invasive Assessment of Liver Fibrosis in Children: Comparison of ShearWave Elastography, Fibrotest and Liver Biopsy</brief_title>
  <acronym>SHEARWAVE</acronym>
  <official_title>Non Invasive Assessment of Liver Fibrosis in Children: Evaluation of Diagnostic Performances of ShearWave Elastography (SWE) and Fibrotest®/ Fibromax® by Comparison With Fibrosis Score on Liver Biopsy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
